sequenceDiagram
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant W as Job Worker
    participant TTS as edge-tts
    participant PX as Pexels/Pixabay
    participant NB as nano banana (fallback)
    participant FF as FFmpeg

    FE->>API: POST /video {mode:b, voice}
    API->>W: render_mode_b job
    loop each scene
        W->>TTS: speak(scene.text, voice)
        TTS-->>W: scene mp3 + word timings
    end
    loop each scene
        W->>PX: search(visual_hint, orientation)
        alt no usable image
            W->>NB: generate(visual_hint)
        end
    end
    W->>W: word timings → phrase-grouped ASS + SRT
    W->>FF: Ken Burns clips → xfade concat → audio → burn ASS
    FF-->>W: output.mp4 + credits.txt
    W-->>FE: done → player + download
